reviewText: Good newaza techniques on this dvd, but material is not very organized, and there is not a whole lot of explanation.  That being said, the material on this dvd interests me in the other newaza dvd in this series.  I'm likely to order it.

Okada Sensei is one of the last living pupil of the legendary Oda Sensei. Okada is as a bridge that introduce us in the original Judo Ne Waza. I think that Okada Sensei is one of the living treasure of judo, both for his technical value than for his very generous teaching.
